1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,810
Life on replay, learned it all online,

2
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:14,769
Like and subscribe, but you won’t own my
mind.

3
00:00:14,919 --> 00:00:19,729
Raw and unfiltered, fame took a shot,

4
00:00:19,879 --> 00:00:24,688
Digital kid, but I can’t be bought.

5
00:00:24,838 --> 00:00:29,648
Got Crocs on stage; a bright-lit room,

6
00:00:29,798 --> 00:00:34,607
I bear witness to tilt and the dinner
gloom.

7
00:00:34,757 --> 00:00:39,567
Pillows too puffy, silence too loud,

8
00:00:39,717 --> 00:00:44,527
Tuned my strings while avoiding the crowd.

9
00:00:44,677 --> 00:00:49,486
[electric violin]

10
00:00:49,636 --> 00:00:54,446
Twelve dollars a week, one tucked in my
sleeve,

11
00:00:54,596 --> 00:00:59,405
Spend eleven on stuff I don’t really need.

12
00:00:59,555 --> 00:01:04,365
Still got my grip, still seeing it
through,

13
00:01:04,515 --> 00:01:09,324
Famous from birth, my name is Lily Roo.

14
00:01:09,474 --> 00:01:14,284
Still ride with the carpool crowd,

15
00:01:14,434 --> 00:01:19,244
Hop out early, skip the paint, stay proud.

16
00:01:19,394 --> 00:01:24,203
Dad’s van smells good but don’t play the
part—

17
00:01:24,353 --> 00:01:29,163
Gifts from the neighbor feel oddly like
art.

18
00:01:29,313 --> 00:01:34,122
Still clean my room, still pack my food,

19
00:01:34,272 --> 00:01:39,082
No gold-leaf mirror can shift my mood.

20
00:01:39,232 --> 00:01:44,042
They say I shine—well maybe I do,

21
00:01:44,192 --> 00:01:49,001
But I still take the trash out too.

22
00:01:49,151 --> 00:01:53,961
Twelve dollars a week, one tucked in my
sleeve,

23
00:01:54,111 --> 00:01:58,920
Spend eleven on stuff I don’t really need.

24
00:01:59,070 --> 00:02:03,880
Still got my grip, still seeing it
through,

25
00:02:04,030 --> 00:02:08,839
Famous from birth, my name is Lily Roo.

26
00:02:08,989 --> 00:02:13,799
They’re pulling me towards neon dreams,

27
00:02:13,949 --> 00:02:18,759
But home is a room where lights never
leave.

28
00:02:18,909 --> 00:02:23,718
Bright enough already, no need for your
spark,

29
00:02:23,868 --> 00:02:28,678
My stage, my rules, I thrive in the dark.

30
00:02:28,828 --> 00:02:33,637
Born into whispers, raised to shout,

31
00:02:33,787 --> 00:02:38,597
Never buying in, won’t sell out.

32
00:02:38,747 --> 00:02:43,556
Twelve bucks weekly keeps me clear,

33
00:02:43,706 --> 00:02:48,516
Bearing witness, why I’m here.
